            <span class="feature-text">‡∏Ñ‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏°‡∏¥‡∏ä‡∏ä‡∏±‡πà‡∏ô‡∏™‡∏π‡∏á‡∏™‡∏∏‡∏î {{ $package->max_commission }}%</span>
