            <div class="order-items-card">
                <h3 class="card-title">üì¶ ‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏™‡∏¥‡∏ô‡∏Ñ‡πâ‡∏≤</h3>
                <div class="space-y-4">
