‚öôÔ∏è Vendor Settings

¬∑ ‡∏ï‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á‡∏Ñ‡πà‡∏≤‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏Ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞‡πÇ‡∏õ‡∏£‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå
¬∑ ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏π‡∏•‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏à‡πà‡∏≤‡∏¢‡πÄ‡∏á‡∏¥‡∏ô‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞‡∏ö‡∏±‡∏ç‡∏ä‡∏µ‡∏ò‡∏ô‡∏≤‡∏Ñ‡∏≤‡∏£
¬∑ ‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏ï‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á‡∏Ñ‡πà‡∏≤‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡πÅ‡∏à‡πâ‡∏á‡πÄ‡∏ï‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏ô

Security & Validation

```php
// Policies ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö Vendor Zone
class ProductPolicy
{
    public function viewAny(User $user): bool
    {
        return $user->hasRole('seller');
    }

    public function update(User $user, Product $product): bool
    {
        return $user->id === $product->seller_id;
    }
}

class OrderPolicy
{
    public function viewVendorOrders(User $user, Order $order): bool
    {
        return $order->items()->whereHas('product', function($query) use ($user) {
            $query->where('seller_id', $user->seller->id);
        })->exists();
    }
}
```

Performance Optimizations

```php
// Eager Loading ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö Vendor Queries
$orders = Order::with([
    'items.product:seller_id', 
    'customer',
    'statusHistory'
])->whereHas('items.product', function($query) use ($vendorId) {
    $query->where('seller_id', $vendorId);
})->paginate(20);

// Caching ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏™‡∏ñ‡∏¥‡∏ï‡∏¥
$stats = Cache::remember("vendor_stats_{$vendorId}", 300, function() use ($vendorId) {
    return [
        'total_sales' => Order::vendorSales($vendorId)->sum('total_amount'),
        'total_orders' => Order::vendorOrders($vendorId)->count(),
        // ... other stats
    ];
});
```

Responsive Design

¬∑ Mobile-first approach
¬∑ Breakpoints: sm (640px), md (768px), lg (1024px), xl (1280px)
¬∑ Touch-friendly interfaces ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏°‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏ñ‡∏∑‡∏≠
¬∑ Optimized images ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞ lazy loading

Accessibility Features

¬∑ ARIA labels ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞ roles
¬∑ Keyboard navigation support
